frames.caption: A majestic wolf stands on a snowy cliff, its fur ruffled by the wind, while a hawk perches beside it. The background features a dramatic mountain landscape with swirling snow and a flock of birds in flight.
frames.description: The scene depicts a powerful and serene moment in a snowy mountain setting. A wolf and a hawk are positioned prominently on a rocky outcrop, surrounded by a dynamic flurry of snow and birds.

frames.caption: A mythical creature with the body of a wolf and the wings and talons of an eagle stands majestically on a rocky cliff. The creature gazes intently into the distance, exuding a sense of power and dominance. The sky is dark and moody, enhancing the dramatic atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical setting where a hybrid creature, part wolf and part eagle, is perched on a rugged cliff. The environment suggests a mythical or otherworldly context, with an emphasis on the creature's commanding presence.
